al-stores-reversion-cpg-inevitable-hurt-financials\">hold rating</a> for Casey\u2019s General Stores (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CASY\" title=\"Casey's General Stores, Inc.\">CASY</a></span>) when I wrote about it last year as I expected fuel margins (cents per gallon [CPG]) to see normalization given the weak demand outlook, which would drag down</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1371981216/image_1371981216.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745503-caseys-general-stores-high-valuation-appears-to-have-already-priced-in-the-upside", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 10:55:59", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745501", "title": "Brown-Forman Corporation: Unlikely To Meet Organic Sales Growth Guidance", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289415723/image_1289415723.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Gold liquid\" data-id=\"1289415723\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8170px\" height=\"6119px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289415723/image_1289415723.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289415723/image_1289415723.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289415723/image_1289415723.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289415723/image_1289415723.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289415723/image_1289415723.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289415723/image_1289415723.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289415723/image_1289415723.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289415723/image_1289415723.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jonathan Knowles</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment summary</h2> <p>My <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4720728-brown-forman-stock-price-likely-to-stay-range-bound-maintain-hold-rating\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4720728-brown-forman-stock-price-likely-to-stay-range-bound-maintain-hold-rating\" target=\"_blank\">previous investment thought</a> on Brown-Forman Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BF.B\" title=\"Brown-Forman Corporation\">BF.B</a></span>, <span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BF.A\" title=\"Brown-Forman Corporation\">BF.A</a></span>) (published on 12th September) was a hold rating because I did not expect growth to see any improvements, given that there were many indicators that suggest so. In this</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289415723/image_1289415723.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745501-brown-forman-corporation-unlikely-to-meet-organic-sales-growth-guidance", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 10:50:11", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745499", "title": "SLVP: Silver Production Is Not Growing", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184404306/image_184404306.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A huge mining superpit on a sunny day\" data-id=\"184404306\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"401px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalp