d": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745496", "title": "Western Union: Deep Value And Dividend Income", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Western Union Office in Prague.\" data-id=\"1943169915\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">VIDOK</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>The Western Union Company provides money movement and payment services worldwide, focused mostly on consumer cross border money transfers and consumer financial services including bill payment, money orders, and digital wallets. The company started out in communication services but has transformed over</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745496-western-union-deep-value-and-dividend-income", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 10:15:15", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745502", "title": "Could A New Misery Index Help Explain The Election Outcome?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oversized vote and ballot box surrounded by people\" data-id=\"2158306529\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"987px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In 1970, everyone was feeling bad about the economy. How bad? To put a number to the pervasively negative vibe, Arthur Okun created the \"misery index:\" the sum of inflation and unemployment rates.</p> <p>But now everyone is puzzled. Why</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745502-new-misery-index-help-explain-election-outcome", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 10:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745493", "title": "Micron Q1 Review: Strong AI Demand Means I'm Still Bullish (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Taiwan Micron Technology Company plant.\" data-id=\"1660789089\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fet